{"id":"shemariah","term":"Shemariah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Whom Jehovah guards. (1.) One who joined David at Ziklag (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 12:5\">1 Chr. 12:5</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 10:32\">Ezra 10:32</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 10:41\">41</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 12:5","Ezra 10:32","Ezra 10:41"]}